pkgmetadata.longdescription:
Multivariate Probabilities of Scale Mixtures of Multivariate
Normal Distributions via the Genz and Bretz (2002) QRSVN Method
// Generates multivariate subgaussian stable probabilities
using the QRSVN algorithm as detailed in Genz and Bretz (2002)
DOI:10.1198/106186002394 but by sampling positive stable
variates not chi/sqrt(nu).
